'''查理·柯士甸'''（{{lang-en|'''Charlie Austin'''}}，{{bd|1989年|7月5日|catIdx=Austin, Charlie}}）是[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[前鋒_(足球)|前鋒]]，現時被[[英超|英超]]球會[[西布罗姆维奇足球俱乐部|西布朗]]外借至[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[女王公园巡游者足球俱乐部|女王公园巡游者]]。

==生平==
===球會===
====早年====
柯士甸出生於[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[東南英格蘭|東南部]][[伯克郡|伯克郡]]的[[民政教區|民政教區]][[亨格福德|亨格福德]]（Hungerford），幼年時參加[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]的青訓系統，曾效力當地的[[Thatcham_Town_F.C.|塔咸鎮]]（Thatcham Town）及家鄉球隊[[Hungerford_Town_F.C.|亨格福德鎮]]（Hungerford Town）。其後舉家遷徙到[[西南英格蘭|西南部]][[多塞特郡|多塞特郡]]的[[市鎮|沿海渡假市鎮]][[伯恩茅斯|伯恩茅斯]]（Bournemouth），他因而就近轉投半[[職業|職業]]「威塞克斯聯賽超聯組」（Wessex League Premier Division）的[[Poole_Town_F.C.|普爾城]]（Poole Town），同時在父親開設的建築公司擔任砌磚的工作。

2008/09年球季柯士甸為普爾城在各項-{比}-賽合共上陣42場及射入驚人的48個入球<small><ref>{{cite web |language=en |title=Poole Town Player Statistics 2008/09 |url=http://www.poole-townfc.co.uk/Player%20Stats/player_stats_0809.html |accessdate=2009-10-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091208020326/http://www.poole-townfc.co.uk/Player%20Stats/player_stats_0809.html |archivedate=2009-12-08 }}</ref></small>，普爾城順利贏得聯賽及[[Dorset_Senior_Cup|多塞特高級盃]]（Dorset Senior Cup）[[雙料冠軍|雙料冠軍]]，而柯士甸亦成為聯賽神射手。

====史雲頓====
普爾城於2009年7月8日應邀與[[英乙|英乙]]球會[[伯恩茅斯足球俱乐部|般尼茅夫]]進行季前[[熱身賽|熱身賽]]，柯士甸以頭球先拔頭籌，協助球隊2-1獲勝<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.afcb.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10324~1717248,00.html |title=POOLE TOWN 2 AFC BOURNEMOUTH 1 |publisher=[[伯恩茅斯足球俱乐部|''afcb.co.uk'']] |date=2009-07-08 |accessdate=2010-02-03 |archive-date=2020-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200516114706/https://www.afcb.co.uk/page/newsdetail/0,,10324~1717248,00.html/ |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。般尼茅夫領隊[[埃迪·霍維|埃迪·霍維]]隨即安排柯士甸隨隊跟操，期間柯士甸仍然為普爾城上陣，於8場聯賽及3場[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]的-{比}-賽轟入18球之多<small><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.poole-townfc.co.uk/Player%20Stats/player_stats_0910.html |title=Poole Town Player Statistics 2009/10 |accessdate=2010-02-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091208020137/http://www.poole-townfc.co.uk/Player%20Stats/player_stats_0910.html |archivedate=2009-12-08 }}</ref></small>，但由於般尼茅夫被禁制買賣球員<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/bournemouth/8225780.stm |title=Cherries defiant as embargo stays |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-08-28 |accessdate=2010-02-05 |archive-date=2019-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190828162213/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/bournemouth/8225780.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，沒法可以羅致柯士甸<small><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.bournemouthecho.co.uk/sport/football/4649747.Austin_s_Robins_move_is_on_the_cards/ |title=Austin's Robins move is on the cards |publisher=Bournemouth Daily Echo |date=26 September 2009 |accessdate=2010-02-04 |archive-date=2017-07-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170707164952/http://www.bournemouthecho.co.uk/sport/football/4649747.Austin_s_Robins_move_is_on_the_cards/ |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

柯士甸在9月獲[[英甲|英甲]]球會[[斯温登足球俱乐部|史雲頓]]提供試訓機會，在隨隊跟操數星期及為預備隊上陣對[[斯旺西城足球俱乐部|史雲斯]]射入一球後，於10月2日動筆簽約加盟史雲頓，為期直至[[2009年至2010年英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|球季]]結束，轉會費金額沒有透露，據報為5萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]，柯士甸放棄其建築工作，從[[英格蘭足球聯賽系統|第九級]]的「威塞克斯聯賽超聯組」連跳6級升上第三級的英甲聯賽，正式成為一名[[職業|職業]]球員<small><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.swindontownfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10341~1816187,00.html |title=Charlie Austin Deal Complete |publisher=[[斯温登足球俱乐部|''swindontownfc.co.uk'']] |date=2009-10-02 |accessdate=2010-02-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100213084413/http://www.swindontownfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0%2C%2C10341~1816187%2C00.html |archivedate=2010-02-13 }}</ref></small>。

史雲頓看中柯士甸的背後得力於班主[[Andrew_Fitton|安德鲁·菲顿]]（Andrew Fitton），他是[[歐洲足協|歐洲足協]]B級教練，並在業餘聯賽中擔任球證，在他主吹的一場-{比}-賽中注意到年僅15歲的柯士甸，兩年後柯士甸加盟由菲顿出任班主的亨格福德鎮。在柯士甸離隊後，菲顿仍然經常留意他的動向，在入主史雲頓後，再度將柯士甸收歸旗下。

10月6日柯士甸首次上陣，於[[英格蘭聯賽錦標|英格蘭聯賽錦標]]作客對[[埃克塞特城足球俱乐部|艾斯特城]]在完場前後補登場，球賽以1-1結束，需以[[互射十二碼|互射十二碼]]定勝負，史雲頓以4-3獲勝，柯士甸沒有被包括在首輪主射的球員名單內<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/8284815.stm |title=Exeter 1-1 Swindon |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-10-06 |accessdate=2010-02-04 |archive-date=2019-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190831142945/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/8284815.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。柯士甸返回預備隊，10月13日對[[谢斯伯利足球俱乐部|梳士貝利]]射入一球協助球隊大勝3-0<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.swindontownfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10341~1824645,00.html |title=FT: SALISBURY 0 SWINDON RES 3 |publisher=[[斯温登足球俱乐部|''swindontownfc.co.uk'']] |date=2009-10-13 |accessdate=2010-02-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091016022726/http://www.swindontownfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10341~1824645,00.html |archivedate=2009年10月16日 |df= }}</ref></small>；兩場入兩場的出色表現獲得球員發展主管[[David_Byrne_(footballer_born_1961)|大衛·拜尼]]（David Byrne）的讚賞，認為此子即將晉身一隊<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.swindontownfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10341~1830918,00.html |title=AUSTIN NOT FAR FROM FIRST TEAM DEBUT |publisher=[[斯温登足球俱乐部|''swindontownfc.co.uk'']] |date=2009-10-20 |accessdate=2010-02-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100111141559/http://www.swindontownfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10341~1830918,00.html |archivedate=2010年1月11日 |df= }}</ref></small>；10月20日柯士甸再為預備隊射入兩球，以3-2僅勝[[普利茅斯足球俱乐部|普利茅夫]]，保持為預備隊上陣3場均取得入球的優良紀錄<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.swindontownfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10341~1831686,00.html |title=TOWN 3 ARGYLE 2 |publisher=[[斯温登足球俱乐部|''swindontownfc.co.uk'']] |date=2009-10-20 |accessdate=2010-02-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100108103043/http://www.swindontownfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10341~1831686,00.html |archivedate=2010年1月8日 |df= }}</ref></small>。

10月24日柯士甸首次在[[英格蘭足球聯賽|聯賽]]上陣，作客對[[诺里奇城足球俱乐部|诺里奇城]]下半場72分鐘後補入替<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8306854.stm |title=Norwich 1-0 Swindon |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-10-24 |accessdate=2010-02-04 |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227010958/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8306854.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；在再獲派兩次後補上陣後，於11月21日首次獲派正選上陣，作客出戰[[卡莱尔联足球俱乐部|卡素爾]]，僅用了3分鐘便證明其射手本色，射入個人首個聯賽入球兼致勝球，1-0奏凱而回<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8353322.stm |title=Carlisle 0-1 Swindon |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-11-21 |accessdate=2010-02-04 |archive-date=2019-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190903004330/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8353322.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，賽後獲領隊[[Danny_Wilson_(footballer)|丹尼·威爾遜]]（Danny Wilson）點名稱讚<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11719_5716209,00.html |title=Wilson delighted with Austin |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-11-24 |accessdate=2010-02-04 |archive-date=2017-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216132218/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11719_5716209,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，而他亦與其父親戲言本季可以射入15球。在接著的10場-{比賽}-柯士甸再轟入9球，於11場正選上陣射入10球，僅有兩場掛零，於2010年1月26日史雲頓本季主場最多觀眾前面對領頭羊[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]]，柯士甸再次先開紀錄，協助球隊大勝3-0<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8450995.stm |title=Swindon 3-0 Leeds United |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-01-26 |accessdate=2010-02-04 |archive-date=2019-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190909053704/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8450995.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，當時[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U21]]領隊[[斯图尔特·皮尔斯|皮雅斯]]亦在場觀看，對柯士甸的表現大表驚訝，其後更派出球探監察柯士甸的進度<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/8530659.stm |title=England U21 scouts watch Swindon's Charlie Austin |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-02-23 |accessdate=2010-02-24 |archive-date=2019-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190909045144/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/8530659.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

在射入兩球以3-2擊敗[[莱顿东方足球俱乐部|奧連特]]後<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8377169.stm |title=Swindon 3-2 Leyton Orient |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-12-05 |accessdate=2010-02-04 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307055947/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8377169.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，柯士甸表示希望球迷支持自己，而不是作為季前離隊的[[西蒙·考克斯|西蒙·考克斯]]的代替品<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11719_5754029,00.html |title=Austin out to make mark |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-12-07 |accessdate=2010-02-04 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308011129/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11719_5754029,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。炙手可熱的柯士甸成為多支球隊羅致的目標，球探紛紛擁到球隊觀察他的表現<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5814317,00.html |title=Austin attracting interest |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-12-31 |accessdate=2010-02-04 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309135047/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5814317,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]、[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|諾定咸森林]]及[[伊普斯维奇城足球俱乐部|葉士域治]]均表示興趣<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11719_5843873,00.html |title=Austin to be offered new deal |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-01-08 |accessdate=2010-02-04}}</ref></small>，但他不為所動，而史雲頓亦啟動合約條款，於2010年2月2日延長合約兩年半<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/8494085.stm |title=Striker Charlie Austin commits future to Swindon Town |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-02-02 |accessdate=2010-02-04 |archive-date=2019-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190903220156/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/8494085.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，他表示會盡力協助球隊爭取升班<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11719_5921277,00.html |title=Austin vows to cement promotion |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-02-06 |accessdate=2010-02-10 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309153946/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11719_5921277,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。柯士甸於3月份6場賽事轟入3球，在4月19日獲選為[[英格蘭足球聯賽|可口可樂聯賽]][[2009年至2010年英格蘭足球甲級聯賽#聯賽每月最青年球員|3月最佳青年球員]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.football-league.co.uk/footballleaguenews/20100419/austin-claims-young-player-prize_2246528_2028769 |title=Austin claims Young Player Prize |publisher=[[英格蘭足球聯賽|''football-league.co.uk'']] |date=2010-04-19 |accessdate=2010-11-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100423015034/http://www.football-league.co.uk/footballleaguenews/20100419/austin-claims-young-player-prize_2246528_2028769 |archivedate=2010-04-23 }}</ref>。

2010年9月11日主場1-0擊敗[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|修咸頓]]中，柯士甸射入唯一入球為史雲頓帶來球季首勝<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8967856.stm |title=Swindon 1-0 Southampton |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-09-11 |accessdate=2011-01-29 |archive-date=2019-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190828193850/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8967856.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但稍後與對方門將[[奇雲·戴維斯|奇雲·戴維斯]]（Kelvin Davis）碰撞後[[肩膀|肩膀]][[脫臼|脫臼]]離場，賽後證實無需動[[手術|手術]]治理<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/8993451.stm |title=Swindon striker Charlie Austin will not need surgery |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-09-15 |accessdate=2011-01-29 |archive-date=2019-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190905050132/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/8993451.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。養傷超過1個月才於10月16日作客4-5負於[[皮特堡联足球俱乐部|彼德堡]]復出，他射入[[十二碼|十二碼]]一度為球隊扳平4-4<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/9075106.stm |title=Peterborough 5-4 Swindon |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-10-16 |accessdate=2011-01-29 |archive-date=2021-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124071208/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/9075106.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其後7場賽事射入6球，他表示是受到[[克雷格·贝拉米|克雷格·贝拉米]]一篇文章的鼓舞，文中稱：『如果你全力以赴，運氣與機會陸續有來。』<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/9194904.stm |title=Swindon's Charlie Austin inspired by Bellamy article |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-11-16 |accessdate=2011-01-29 |archive-date=2019-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190903051330/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/9194904.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。史雲頓亦尋求與柯士甸續約<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/9183945.stm |title=Swindon Town look to extend Charlie Austin deal |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-11-12 |accessdate=2011-01-29 |archive-date=2019-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190909001803/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/9183945.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，季內已射入14球，史雲頓拒絕[[赫尔城足球俱乐部|侯城]]的出價後又接獲[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]的問價，柯士甸表示未來動向不明朗<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/9312165.stm |title=Swindon Town's Charlie Austin unsure over future |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-12-22 |accessdate=2011-01-29 |archive-date=2019-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190828084821/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/9312165.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

多支[[英冠|英冠]]球隊有意在2011年冬季[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]羅致柯士甸，他於1月18日向史雲頓提出轉會要求<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/9365140.stm |title=Swindon Town's Charlie Austin hands in transfer request |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-01-18 |accessdate=2011-01-29 |archive-date=2019-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190901222815/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/9365140.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[英超|英超]]球會[[黑池足球會|黑池]]最先出價<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/9372956.stm |title=Blackpool bid for Swindon Town striker Charlie Austin |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-01-26 |accessdate=2011-01-29 |archive-date=2019-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190903015023/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/9372956.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[伊普斯维奇城足球俱乐部|葉士域治]]、[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|般尼]]及[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|修咸頓]]加入爭奪<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6704352,00.html |title=Quartet battle for Austin |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2011-01-27 |accessdate=2011-01-29 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310081903/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6704352,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

====般尼====
史雲頓最先接納[[伊普斯维奇城足球俱乐部|葉士域治]]沒有透露金額的出價，柯士甸獲准與葉士域治商討私人條件<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6704911,00.html |title=Town see Austin bid accepted |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2011-01-27 |accessdate=2011-01-29 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310081909/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6704911,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但未能達成協議，[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|般尼]]隨即介入並獲史雲頓接納出價，於2010年1月28日與柯士甸簽訂三年半合約，轉會費沒有透露<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/9378506.stm |title=Swindon Town striker Charlie Austin joins Burnley |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-01-28 |accessdate=2011-01-29 |archive-date=2020-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200201040849/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/9378506.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，據報初步為120萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]再加附帶條款<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11700_6706379,00.html |title=Clarets to win Austin chase |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2011-01-28 |accessdate=2011-01-29 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310090346/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11700_6706379,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，負責引進柯士甸的般尼新帥正是當年因買賣球員禁令而錯失合作機會的前[[伯恩茅斯足球俱乐部|般尼茅夫]]領隊[[埃迪·霍維|埃迪·霍維]]。2011年8月6日聯賽揭幕戰主場對[[沃特福德足球俱乐部|屈福特]]，下半場後補上陣的柯士甸射入加盟後首球，協助球隊最終扳平2-2完場<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/14351859.stm |title=Burnley 2-2 Watford |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-08-06 |accessdate=2011-08-11 |archive-date=2019-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190829223323/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/14351859.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年11月6日柯士甸在主場對[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]]射入整場賽事的唯一入球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20134364 |title=Burnley 1-0 Leeds United |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2012-11-06 |accessdate=2012-11-17 |archive-date=2014-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140404223716/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20134364 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，開季只用了17場賽事便射入20球，打破球會的紀錄，比舊紀錄少賽8場<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20237543 |title=Burnley striker Charlie Austin reaches 20-goal landmark |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2012-11-07 |accessdate=2012-11-17 |archive-date=2013-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131017161049/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20237543 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年7月9日，新升上[[英超|英超]]作賽的[[赫尔城足球俱乐部|赫尔城]]原與[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|般尼]]達成協議購入柯士甸，但因柯士甸未能通過身體檢查交易告吹<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23238595 |title=Charlie Austin: Burnley striker fails Hull City medical |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2013-07-09 |accessdate=2013-09-27 |archive-date=2015-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150825034221/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23238595 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

====女王公园巡游者====
2013年8月1日，剛降落[[英冠|英冠]]作賽的[[女王公园巡游者足球俱乐部|女王公园巡游者]]與[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|般尼]]達成協議購入柯士甸，轉會費金額沒有透露，合約為期三年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23533841 |title=Charlie Austin: QPR sign Burnley striker for undisclosed fee |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2013-08-01 |accessdate=2013-09-27 |archive-date=2013-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131018055447/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23533841 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年12月6日，重返英超的昆士柏流浪主場迎戰西布朗，查理柯士甸大演帽子戲法，連中三元，出場15次攻入11個聯賽入球，成為英超2014-15年球季半程本土神射手，射手榜排名第三位，僅次曼城射手阿古路及車路士前鋒迪亞高哥斯達，表現令人眼前一亮，入選英格蘭國家足球代表隊之聲亦不絕於耳。

